{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The backend contract is in place now: character refinements can carry a specific base sheet plus structured impact metadata, and the service can distinguish major vs minor refinements instead of treating every chat edit the same. I\u2019m mir...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_118", "text": "The backend contract is in place now: character refinements can carry a specific base sheet plus structured impact metadata, and the service can distinguish major vs minor refinements instead of treating every chat edit the same. I\u2019m mirroring that in the frontend and surfacing the persisted refinement rationale so the chat pane and workspace stay aligned.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 237, "prompt_index": 48, "prompt_name": "47 \u2014 Character Sheet Selection and Refinement via Chat", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T22:59:32-07:00"}
