{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented prompt 47 end to end and checkpointed the code in commit `d7c0df1` (`feat(prompt-47): character refinement via chat`). The backend now supports targeted character refinement actions with persisted `focus_character_names`, `ch...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_247", "text": "Implemented prompt 47 end to end and checkpointed the code in commit `d7c0df1` (`feat(prompt-47): character refinement via chat`). The backend now supports targeted character refinement actions with persisted `focus_character_names`, `change_summary`, and `change_impact`; minor refinements preserve accepted beats by relinking them to the refined sheet, while major refinements invalidate downstream planning. The frontend now exposes those refinement controls in the characters stage, keeps the selected/refined sheet inspectable, and echoes accepted character changes back into chat using durable backend rationale.\n\nVerification included `pytest backend/tests -q` (`155 passed, 5 skipped`), targeted backend/API suites, `npm --prefix frontend test`, `npm --prefix frontend run lint`, `npm --prefix frontend run build`, and a browser spec against the live Docker Compose app that produced [character-refinement-stage.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/character-refinement-stage.png). The required reviewer summary was written as the final step to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/47_character_sheet_selection_and_refinement_via_chat/summary.md). Remaining dirty files are unrelated `.yolopilot` run logs/status files that I left untouched.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 526, "prompt_index": 48, "prompt_name": "47 \u2014 Character Sheet Selection and Refinement via Chat", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T23:18:33-07:00"}
{"color": "bright_black", "emoji": "?", "event_type": "Unkown Event", "message": "{ \"item\": { \"id\": \"item_22\", \"items\": [ { \"completed\": true, \"text\": \"Inspect current character refinement flow across backend, chat intent parsing, hydration, and frontend workspace\" }, { \"completed\": false, \"text\": \"Implement backend s...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_22", "items": [{"completed": true, "text": "Inspect current character refinement flow across backend, chat intent parsing, hydration, and frontend workspace"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Implement backend support for structured character refinement targets/change impact and downstream invalidation behavior"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Update frontend chat/UI flows to expose refined character metadata and refresh indicators without losing structured state"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Add and run targeted tests, broader checks, and browser-based verification; commit checkpoints"}, {"completed": false, "text": "Write the required reviewer summary markdown as the final action"}], "type": "todo_list"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 527, "prompt_index": 48, "prompt_name": "47 \u2014 Character Sheet Selection and Refinement via Chat", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T23:18:34-07:00"}
